<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Houston_Chronicle&action=edit&section=24.php.html" title="Edit section: Prices">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Prices">Prices</span></h2>
<p><i>Chronicle</i> prices are $1 daily; $2.50 ($3 outside Harris/neighbouring counties) Sunday/Thanksgiving Day.</p>
